    "content": "It was a typical day in the life of a Victorian mother, as she sat at her computer, scrolling through social media feeds and checking emails. She had just finished cooking dinner for her family when she heard a loud crash from the kitchen. She rushed to investigate, only to find that her laptop had been smashed into a million pieces. The screen was shattered, and the keyboard was bent in several places. Her heart sank as she realized that she would have to replace it all over again."
